    "# 第二章：字符串和文本"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2.1 使用多个界定符分割字符串"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "问题：需要将一个字符串分割为多个字段，但是分隔符（还有周围的空格）并不是固定的"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "解决方案：string对象的split方法只适应于非常简单的字符串分割情形，它并不允许有多个分隔符或者分隔符周围不确定的空格\n",
    "，当你需要更加灵活的切割字符串的时候，最好使用re.split()方法"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['asdf', 'fjdk', 'afed', 'fjed', 'asdf', 'foo']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 2,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "line = 'asdf fjdk;  afed, fjed,asdf,   foo'\n",
    "import re\n",
    "re.split(r'[;,\\s]\\s*', line)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "分隔符可以是逗号，分好或者空格，并且后面紧跟着任意个的空格"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "当你使用re.split函数时候，需要特别注意的是正则表达式中是否包含一个括号捕获分组，如果使用捕获分组，那么被匹配的文本也将出现结果列表中，比如"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['asdf', ' ', 'fjdk', ';', 'afed', ',', 'fjed', ',', 'asdf', ',', 'foo']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 3,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fields = re.split(r'(;|,|\\s)\\s*', line)\n",
    "fields"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "获取分割字符在某些情况下也是有用的，比如"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "(['asdf', 'fjdk', 'afed', 'fjed', 'asdf', 'foo'],\n",
       " [' ', ';', ',', ',', ',', ''])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 4,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "values = fields[::2]\n",
    "delimiters = fields[1::2] + ['']\n",
    "values,delimiters"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "'asdf fjdk;afed,fjed,asdf,foo'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "''.join(v+d for v, d in zip(values, delimiters))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "如果你不想保留分割字符串到结果列表去，但仍然需要使用括号来分组正则表达式的话，确保你的分组是非捕获分组\n",
    "形如，(?:......)，比如："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['asdf', 'fjdk', 'afed', 'fjed', 'asdf', 'foo']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 6,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "re.split(r'(?:,|;|\\s)\\s*', line) #这个跟In2的区别是？"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2.2 字符串开头或结尾匹配"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "问题：你需要指定的文本模式去检查字符串的开头或者结尾，比如，文件后缀，URL Scheme等"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "解决方案：简单方法是使用str.startswith() str.endswith()"
   ]
