   "source": [
    "## 2.3 用shell通配符匹配字符串"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "问题：你想使用linux shell中的常用的通配符，比如，*.py,Dat[0-9]*.csv等去匹配文本字符串"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "解决方法：fnmatch模块提供两个函数 fnmatch和fnmatchcase，可以用来实现这样的匹配，比如"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "(True, True, True)"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 9,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from fnmatch import fnmatch, fnmatchcase\n",
    "\n",
    "fnmatch('foo.txt', '*.txt'), fnmatch('too.txt', '?oo.txt'),fnmatch('Dat45.csv', 'Dat[0-9]*')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['Dat1.csv', 'Dat2.csv']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 10,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "names = ['Dat1.csv', 'Dat2.csv', 'config.ini', 'foo.py']\n",
    "[name for name in names if fnmatch(name, 'Dat*.csv')]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "fnmatch对底层操作系统大小写敏感，如果对这个区别很在意，可以使用fnmatchcase来代替，它完全使用你的模式大小写匹配，比如"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "True"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 14,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fnmatch('foo.txt', '*.TXT')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "False"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 15,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fnmatchcase('foo.txt','*.TXT')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "这两个函数通常会被忽略的一个特性是在处理非文件名的字符串时，它们是有用的，比如，一个街道\n",
    "数据"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 16,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "address = [\n",
