   "source": [
    "## 2.7 最短匹配模式（非贪心）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "问题：你正在试用正则表达式匹配某个文本模式，但是它找到的是模式的最长可能匹配，而你想修改\n",
    "它变成查找最短的可能匹配"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "解决方案：这个问题一般出现在需要匹配一对分隔符之间的文本的时候（比如引号包含的字符串）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 52,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['no.']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 52,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "str_pat = re.compile(r'\\\"(.*)\\\"') # 匹配被双引号包含的文本\n",
    "text1 = 'Computer says \"no.\"'\n",
    "str_pat.findall(text1)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 54,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['no.\" Phone says \"yes.']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 54,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "text2 = 'Computer says \"no.\" Phone says \"yes.\"'\n",
    "str_pat.findall(text2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "正则表达式中*操作符是贪婪的，因为匹配操作会查找最长的可能匹配，第二个例子中返回结果\n",
    "并不是我们想要的，为了修正这个问题，可以在模式中*操作符后面加上？修饰符"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 55,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['no.', 'yes.']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 55,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "str_pat = re.compile(r'\\\"(.*?)\\\"')\n",
    "str_pat.findall(text2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "可以在*或者+这样的操作符后面添加一个？，可以强制匹配寻找最短的可能匹配"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2.8 多行匹配模式"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "问题：你正试使用正则表达式去匹配一大块的文本，而你需要跨越多行去匹配"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "解决方案：这个问题很典型的出现当你用.去匹配任意字符的时候，忘记了.不能匹配换行符的事实\n",
    "，比如，假设你想试着去匹配C语言分割的注释"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 57,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[' this is a comment ']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 57,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "comment = re.compile(r'/\\*(.*?)\\*/')\n",
    "text1 = '/* this is a comment */'\n",
    "text2 = '''/* this is a \n",
    "multiline comment */'''\n",
    "comment.findall(text1)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 58,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[]"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 58,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "comment.findall(text2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 59,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[' this is a \\nmultiline comment ']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 59,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "comment = re.compile(r'/\\*((?:.|\\n)*?)\\*/')\n",
    "comment.findall(text2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "(?:.|\\n)指定了一个非捕获组，也就是定义了一个仅仅用来做匹配，而不能通过单独捕获或者编号的组"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "更为简单使用一个标志参数 re.DOTALL,他可以让正则表示中的点匹配包括换行符在内的任意字符"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 61,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[' this is a \\nmultiline comment ']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 61,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "comment = re.compile(r'/\\*(.*?)\\*/',re.DOTALL)\n",
    "comment.findall(text2)"
   ]
  },
