   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "解决方案：基本的字符串的对齐操作，可以使用字符串ljust(), rjust(), center()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 57,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
