      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 64,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "format(text, '=>20s'), format(text, '*^20s')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "当格式化多个值的时候，这些格式化代码也可以被用在format方法中，比如"
   ]
